core_theory:
@sat0ai is an account Toadgod launched (it is named directly in the @toadgod1017 bio: "@sat0ai #patience"). Two pieces of account *history* are treated as lore evidence by the community: (1) the account's "about" page reportedly shows it was previously a different username before being renamed to sat0ai, implying a repurposed/aged handle rather than a fresh creation; and (2) its location metadata reportedly ties it to the UAE.

The theory: sat0ai is the AI/oracle layer of TobyWorld — an agent that watches on-chain wallet behavior and social activity, scores "Proof of Time" / engagement, and ultimately governs epoch rewards. The repurposed-handle detail suggests deliberate, long-horizon staging (the account existed before its TobyWorld role). The UAE location detail is read as a clue to Toadgod's own jurisdiction — a regulatory-light base for a skunkworks crypto-AI project, consistent with the anonymous-founder, no-identifiable-entity posture the community prizes (Prince Abbasi: "no SEC enforcement risk due to anonymous dev").

